        "content": "Project: Predictive Maintenance Alert Automation.\n\nPlatform: n8n (Low-code workflow engine).\n\nFrequency: Runs every 15 minutes (Schedule Trigger).\n\nGoal: Eliminate machine downtime through proactive, real-time health monitoring."
