    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": " Ingestion & Logging\nSource: Fetches data from ThingSpeak IoT Platform.\n\nParameters: Monitors Temperature, Vibration, and Pressure.\n\nAudit Trail: Every reading (Normal or Alert) is automatically logged in Google Sheets for long-term history and compliance."
