    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "Smart Alert Logic\nThe \"ALERT\" Thresholds:\n\nTemp: > 70°C\n\nVibration: > 4 mm/s\n\nPressure: < 90 psi\n\nValidation: Uses a JavaScript Node to normalize data and ensure alerts only trigger when strict conditions are met (reducing false alarms).",
